nodes.title: Instructions
widgets_values:
# Consistent Face v1.2

## Required model files
- Flux Dev
- Flux Dev Fill
- LoRA: flux1-depth-dev-lora; chinfixer-2000; skin-texture-style-v5 (or alternatives)
- Ultralytics: Eyes.pt or Eyeful_v2-Paired.pt

## How it works 
### (green nodes are the settings' nodes of the workflow you can change)
- Upload a reference 3x3 grid image (mine: https://imgur.com/a/ZEZp82J )
- Set flux1-depth_dev_lora strength (default 0.75).
- Set FluxGuidance (default 4.0).
- Set Sampler and Scheduler (default euler/beta).
- Set Steps (default 35).
- Set Seed (random or fixed).
- Select an upscale model and set upscale_by 3 (default model 4x_RealWebPhoto_v4).
- Modify the Prompt to describe in detail the subject appearance (skin tone, physique, face shape, hair and eyes).
- In the Step 2: Set the strength of the Skin LoRA (default 0.75)
- Set the dishonesty_factor for detail, lower negative numbers mean higher detail (default -0.05 - use this with care, it may change the image a lot!)
- Start generating the images.

The workflow will upscale by 3 an image and then generate 9 images (1024x1024) from it, this mean it has to process FaceDetailer, EyesDetailer, apply Skin Lora and apply Chin-fix Lora for 9 images.  This is why the whole generation will take very long.  It is normal.

### Ultralytics files 
Eyes.pt download link: https://huggingface.co/Tenofas/ComfyUI/resolve/main/ultralytics/bbox/Eyes.pt

Eyeful_v2-Paired.pt download link: https://huggingface.co/Tenofas/ComfyUI/resolve/main/ultralytics/bbox/Eyeful_v2-Paired.pt

This photograph is a composite of nine photographs arranged in a 3x3 grid, featuring the same italian girl in various poses against a plain, muted gray background. 

The girl appears to be in her mid-20s, with fair skin, a fit physique and an square face. The girl has long straight ginger hair with bangs and green eyes. 

The lighting is soft, casting gentle shadows that highlight the contours of her face and body.
